Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:31.38,SONG-05,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H809798&\3a&H35&}我要妨礙你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:34.04,SONG-05,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H809798&\3a&H35&}不需要那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:36.80,SONG-05,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H809798&\3a&H35&}通向幸福的道路
