Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:42.12,SONG-05,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H809798&\3a&H35&}給幸福添上痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:44.96,SONG-05,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H809798&\3a&H35&}不需要那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:47.72,SONG-05,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H809798&\3a&H35&}殘酷的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:50.24,SONG-05,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H809798&\3a&H35&}全部！全部！都不需要！
