Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:06.32,Caligula,,0,0,0,,來吧 用妳的歌聲來指引他們吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:07.85,Caligula,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:09.20,Caligula,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.32,Caligula,,0,0,0,,但是 thorn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:13.32,Caligula,,0,0,0,,答應我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.51,Caligula,,0,0,0,,不要傷害大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:20.04,Caligula,,0,0,0,,嗯 這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:05.84,Caligula,,0,0,0,,這邊也不行 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:11.21,Caligula,,0,0,0,,妳在做什麼 要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:13.17,Caligula,,0,0,0,,好、好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:14.39,Caligula,,0,0,0,,命運！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:19.33,Caligula,,0,0,0,,在這裡遇到你簡直就是命運的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:21.62,Caligula,,0,0,0,,你說對吧 峯澤？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:23.99,Caligula,,0,0,0,,你是誰勒？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:25.15,Caligula,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:28.98,Caligula,,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:31.15,Caligula,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啦！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:35.35,Caligula,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:44.33,Caligula,,0,0,0,,今天能見到妳很開心哦 美...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:46.50,Caligula,,0,0,0,,感覺有點不妙 我們快走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.26,Caligula,,0,0,0,,再見了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:56.68,Caligula,,0,0,0,,再...見...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:02:00.35,Caligula,,0,0,0,,再見...再...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:03.35,Caligula,,0,0,0,,要走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:08.19,Caligula,,0,0,0,,媽媽 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.47,Caligula,,0,0,0,,學長你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:48.31,Caligula,,0,0,0,,給我做好覺悟吧 小姑娘！
